    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''Amadeus,'' a revival of Peter Shaffer's 1980 drama, is to close after the matinee on Sunday at the Music Box Theater, 239 West 45th Street, Manhattan. The play, directed by Sir Peter Hall, will have run for 165 regular performances and 10 previews.</p>
      </block>
